      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor; scoped out per project risk assessment.",
      "rationale": "Test sample characterization beyond standard hematocrit measurement is not required at Model Risk Level 2. Scoped out per credibility plan."
